        "action": "Revoke guidance on social distancing and bubbles in schools",
        "additional_details": "It can also be very stressful for school staff trying to keep them in their bubbles. ALL schools need to go back to normal NO more social distancing NO More Bubbles.",
        "background": "Please stop all social distancing and bubbles in schools because it's affecting children's mental wellbeing and their learning. It's also inhibiting their social skills for interacting with other children in different year groups. Please could we end this now.",
